Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:24.30,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the skies that are still unknown to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.37,Default,op,0,0,0,,I know, you're doing just the same -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:29.94,Default,op,0,0,0,,Dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:35.21,Default,op,0,0,0,,Just a small glow\NFrom those great days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.21,0:00:38.08,Default,op,0,0,0,,Is what dragging you along
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:41.87,Default,op,0,0,0,,Giving you faith and some comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.76,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the sun that scorches badly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:52.13,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only want to see your guise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:53.91,Default,op,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.14,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only watch \NWith tears on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:04.74,Default,op,0,0,0,,As you slowly disappear in this noon haze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.76,Default,op,0,0,0,,We're alone \NWe're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.31,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Walking this world on our own
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.36,0:01:16.53,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}Looking for each other since long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.46,Default,op,0,0,0,,In the end, in the end, \NAfter the day we finally meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:26.97,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord1\blur1\t(2100,2200,\shad3\blur3\c&HABADD8&)\move(360,440,137.25,440,2200,4500)}We won't ever have to say "Goodbye"
