Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:21.81,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:27.44,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:30.40,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:33.28,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:38.47,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:45.38,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:50.76,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:57.64,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:23:04.06,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.13,0:23:13.25,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:18.45,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:21.50,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:24.54,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:30.07,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Queen's Cup 90 finals \Nwere postponed due to the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The match between Gene Ryder and Oka Hiromi \Nwas rescheduled to 1 pm of the following day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your room was empty, \Nso I thought of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like a café au lait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday... At night, \NI've been to Madame Butterfly's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi is two steps away from the final match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know for sure if I should reveal it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly is...\Nprobably retiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your café au lait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:51.93,Default,,0,0,280,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HAC907F&\t(0,1100,\bord0\blur0.55)\c&HFEFEFD&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz360\3a&H2D&\fscx162\fscy137}Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My tomorrow's match is as late as 1 pm.\NCouldn't stand sitting in a hotel the whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I leave here at morning,\NI won't be running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hope for a proper sleep \Nunless I'm in my own bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I absolutely missed mom's cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only 4 o'clock now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well, all the way to the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I recorded every TV broadcast with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Salmon pot will make just well!\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to have a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is salmon pot fine with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Katsura.\NExcuse me, but can I speak to Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Hiromi leave the hotel \Nwithout Mr. Katsura's permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just... \NWanted to make sure she made it there. Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika, Oka's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka came to visit us.\NWaiting for you in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish her the best of luck in tomorrow's finals... \NPlease tell her so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika just now went to take a little nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She deserves some rest, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka! Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, I went to the venue\Nbut found out today's match was postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't at the hotel either.\NSo I headed to your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly retires?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I even went to hers to make certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...\NShe didn't wish to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However, last night \NMidorikawa managed to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhausted, she was sitting there crying softly:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Forgive me. \NI can't play tennis anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And to all of her father, Chairman Ryuzaki's pleas, \Nshe only hung her head in doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You've no idea \Nhow I'm worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it \Nis so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so unsettled with all of this, \NI also cannot play tennis...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I admired her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Only thanks to Madame Butterfly being there for me, \NI managed to come this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole tomorrow's finale bothers me not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If Madame Butterfly quits tennis,\Nthere's nothing else to make me go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In this restaurant...\Ndo you still remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, just like today, \NIt was pouring rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was when I decided that I either become a pro \Nor quit tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a bit confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was having here\Njust as burning-hot coffee with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a decision then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I will try my best no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite the fact it's just the most ordinary roadside restaurant, \Nit became a starting line for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, at that moment,\NI thought so about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if I fail,\Nthis can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just once again come to this restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows,\Nperhaps when it happens, it won't be raining anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is that when it finally does, \Nyou'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not excluded \Nthat the whole restaurant by that time may be no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it's fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What I know for sure is that you were here, \Nand it was pouring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We were drinking burning-hot coffee...\NAnd I needn't not any other truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This was enough to give me courage \Nfor making an important decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,An amazing decision it appeared to me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because... It was because I knew \Nthat even if I fail, I wouldn't lose everything I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The confidence in you being here \Nhas always filled me with courage and confidence once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly's restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you think, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Right now she is desperately \Ntrying her best to recall this place again.
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.81,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}All alone, full of grievous confidence \Nthat no one will come to her special place when she needs it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly has already \Nreturned there once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So now she just needs time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, she'll surely come back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we can, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just have patience and humbly wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad but we can't help her any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Neglected my brilliant training plan \Njust to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How fortunate of you, Todo! \NWithout rain and postponement, you'd never see the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Show at least some professional consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the court!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go, Hiromi. \NOkay? The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Need to make a final push, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In the final round, no retreat is an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the match is over, \Nforget about Ochou and other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the worthy ones can make it to the final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever reaches it becomes obliged \Nto fight for ones who've lost as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, Broir, Morita, Ling,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the losers remain on the court, \Nmanifested in your brilliant fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean to say you forgot them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I remember them all, \Nstill clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up then!\NStand up and get on the court!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And remember \Nto show everyone your ultimate fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(600,0)}Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,To get to the match, we should leave shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to go out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I think today...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rightly so. \NThat's even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever was there before,\Nis all over for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...\NWhy aren't you at the finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It just so happens \Nthat I also decided to stay home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be... \NYou shouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the association chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If not from you, \Nwhom from would winner get her cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,, I am an ordinary man there, \Nreplaceable by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:11:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But today, on such important for you day, \Nright here no one will replace me as your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If today I'm to stay home for the whole afternoon, \NI don't think it'll hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm obliged to help you in any way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is. \NThat's how I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi has every chance \Nof becoming the champion, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you, father, can congratulate such a champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't you looking forward to the day it finally happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For the whole Japanese Tennis Association, \Nand your hopes for Oka. Aren't those your words?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when the dream is about to be fulfilled, \Nyou give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,On Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I tell you just one thing, Reika?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this defeat \Nwas vitally essential for you, Reika.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how else without it, \Ncould you continue your self-development?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Be liberated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you forgive me for what I'll say \Nbecause I see it suitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see the finals. \NTogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No...\NIf you don't want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go. \NI have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika!...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi is doing her best now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I must see her doing so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.61,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself...\NI myself must see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.97,0:12:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you, Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo, do it for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you, Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trust me to make it all okay, Munakata.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka keeps her service-game. The score is tied. \NFrom the very first set, her offensive is fierce!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect hit again!\NOka's return ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did Oka \Nlearn to hit such a ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The world rankings' seventh Gene Ryder \Nlooks not so carefree anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryder approaches the net!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo, human beings meet each other and communicate \Nin a variety of different forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Through a variety of different approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, the tennis approach \Nhelped me meet Oka once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, regardless of Oka's mind, \NI ought to be her coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka is a natural-born player, \Nalthough no one sees prerequisites for it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, in order to get the most out of her tennis, \NI even let her priceless youth be replaced with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's my responsibility now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you perfectly, Munakata.\NI got it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, to teach her tennis... The limit to which \Nthe tennis can be taught to her is already near.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to be a true player...\NWhat does it mean to be a true coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Munakata...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hot temper.\NIs that a world's seventh worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Unknown Oka Hiromi turned out \Nto be a formidable adversary. It's a shock for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo, that would suffice for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Madame Butterfly,\Nthank you very much for everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coach Katsura,\Ntoday, I'm not fighting here alone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could never fight here alone. \NI realized it just recently!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alone, I would never have made it here, \Ndoing my best all this time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I realized it here while chasing the ball!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just that I've been \Nthe most ordinary child all the way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An ordinary child, \Nwho happened to be playing this big match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unbelievable, isn't it?\NI can't believe it myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, I know one for sure - if it weren't for Coach Katsura \Nand Madame Butterfly, Todo and Maki, Chairman Ryuzaki,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiba and Ozaki,\Nand finally...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally... Coach Munakata!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I reached here thanks to everyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, \NI truly believe in it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is the tie-break!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to a twelve-point system, \Nthe first player to score 7 points wins this set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible, Oka! You scored 7 points! \NThe first set is rightfully yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:17:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One more set. Just another set at such a vigorous pace, \Nand for Oka her first Queen title will be no longer a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Never stop, Oka! \NFor certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi's hits...\NI wanted to serve such balls myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Three against zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Match point again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Oka is nothing but one point away from winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryder has no room for error!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Half step onwards more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Champion - Oka Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but didn't you want \Nto show something to me and Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it was on his last day,\Nor maybe a day or two before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Munakata Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote me this, his final letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and read it. \NThe contents are why I wanted to show it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo, however, teaching her tennis... \NThe limit to which tennis can be taught to her is already near.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a true player... \NTo be a true coach, after all, what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm short on time, \Nstill, I spend a lot of it thinking hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One day Oka will become stronger, \Neventually outgrowing even her own tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What should she do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably, when it happens, \Nshe'll need neither me, Daigo, nor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth be told, \Nwe are just a wee bit ahead of Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, what Oka will really need then \Nis someone to walk along with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the difficulties, sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course joy, \Nthey would share together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about tennis only.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka will need someone \Nwhom she can give her... faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In whom she can believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine only such a person \Nwill be a true Oka's coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo, I thus entrust Oka at your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you yourself \Never have to pass this baton to another,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,also make sure to think twice \Nwho you entrust her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Since for an unreliable person like I am... \NOka is too magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In a year...\NNo, even half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka will become a recognized pro, \Nand the high time comes she starts climbing further.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you accept this baton \Nfrom me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot know what lies ahead, \Nbut until then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will surely do my best to become a person \Nreliable enough to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any send-offs you know. \NI'm not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I need to contact you \Nafter you travel through America again, how do I find you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be paying you a call, \Neach time my address shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fine with me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NWhy do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking, \Nmaybe I should go to America too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My pro initiation didn't go well. \NI thought to try my luck getting a licence there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Indeed! \NJust a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting over...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, to celebrate your championship, \NI want to present you with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... that there is nothing else \NI would want now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,15-0!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:09.47,Default,,0,66,20,,{\fade(400,0)\an3\fs35\blur1\bord0\b1}The end
